{
  "stem": "19210.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And whether or not-- I really doubt that that was the main reason that he-- he wished to save the Jews because I believe he saved the Jews because it was his character.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "His conscience did not allow him to see so many people die because they were taken prisoners by judgments and that would be the end of it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So-- so I had the great privilege, the great honor, to meet this great man and I'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I had heard earlier that because interesting enough, next door to our house in Lisbon, we had a-- a- a-- a horseshoe man.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was like, looked like the Jolly Green Giant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a big man with a big belly and his job was horsing shoes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Next door to him was an equestrian school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to play there when we were children, as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And Don Luiz was his name, L-U-I-Z, always asked me when I came back from school to read him the newspapers.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then other people would come in and sit in this little shop-- two or three other guys, I don't even know their names-- and they were listening as I was reading the newspaper.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then they used to-- to debate because they-- they were really Portuguese Portuguese, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They came from a town in the north of Portugal by the name of Guimaraes, G-U-I-M-A-R-A-E-S.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And if you go to visit Portugal today and if you visit Guimaraes, you will see the signs that will say [PORTUGUESE], Portugal was born here.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They're very devoted, very, very Portuguese.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So of course, they didn't particularly care about the war, Hitler, the refugees, the destruction et cetera.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
